sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist / Pipeline User
    participant KFP as KFP API Server
    participant InitC as odh-pipelines-components<br/>(Init Container)
    participant PVC as KFP Pipeline Workspace<br/>(PVC)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as AWS S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OGX as OGX API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrainHub as Kubeflow Training Hub<br/>(ClusterTrainingRuntime)
    participant Milvus as Milvus Vector Store
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant LiteLLM as LiteLLM / LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over InitC,KFP: Startup: Managed Pipeline Registration
    InitC->>InitC: Compile pipeline.py → pipeline.yaml
    InitC->>KFP: Copy YAMLs to /config/managed-pipelines/<br/>(path traversal validated)
    KFP->>KFP: Discover & register managed pipelines

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 1: LLM Fine-Tuning (LoRA/OSFT/SFT)
    User->>KFP: Submit fine-tuning pipeline run
    KFP->>HF: GET model & dataset<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>PVC: Model artifacts & dataset
    KFP->>S3: GET dataset (alternate source)<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>PVC: Dataset files
    KFP->>K8sAPI: POST TrainingJob<br/>Auth: Bearer KUBERNETES_AUTH_TOKEN
    K8sAPI->>TrainHub: Create ClusterTrainingRuntime job
    TrainHub-->>PVC: Trained model checkpoints
    KFP->>KFP: Run lm_eval evaluation<br/>(vLLM in-process)
    KFP->>ModelReg: POST RegisteredModel + ModelVersion<br/>Auth: None (insecure HTTP)
    ModelReg-->>KFP: Registration confirmed
    KFP-->>User: Pipeline run complete

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: AutoGluon Tabular Training
    User->>KFP: Submit AutoML pipeline run
    KFP->>S3: GET CSV dataset<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>PVC: CSV data
    KFP->>KFP: automl_data_loader → split data<br/>(odh-automl image)
    KFP->>KFP: autogluon_models_training<br/>(odh-automl image)
    KFP->>KFP: leaderboard_evaluation<br/>Generate model leaderboard
    KFP-->>User: Leaderboard & trained models

    Note over User,OGX: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization
    User->>KFP: Submit AutoRAG pipeline run
    KFP->>S3: GET documents<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>PVC: Raw documents
    KFP->>KFP: documents_discovery<br/>(odh-autorag image)
    KFP->>KFP: text_extraction (Docling)<br/>(odh-autorag image)
    KFP->>OGX: POST embeddings request<br/>Auth: Bearer OGX_CLIENT_API_KEY
    OGX-->>KFP: Embedding vectors
    KFP->>Milvus: Index vectors<br/>Auth: Configurable
    KFP->>OGX: POST search_space + optimization<br/>Auth: Bearer OGX_CLIENT_API_KEY
    OGX-->>KFP: Optimized RAG patterns
    KFP->>KFP: leaderboard_evaluation + build_responses_api_requests
    KFP-->>User: RAG optimization results

    Note over User,LiteLLM: Flow 4: Synthetic Data Generation
    User->>KFP: Submit SDG pipeline run
    KFP->>LiteLLM: POST generation request<br/>Auth: API Key (LLM_API_KEY)
    LiteLLM-->>KFP: Generated synthetic data
    KFP-->>User: Synthetic dataset
